== Summary

This chapter adds a new <ex>=spi_1lane_stream scope to the
Makefile-driven regression suite: a 5-block TEST.md (preflight + 4
stream prescaler points) and a verify.py that copies the spi.nw
stream-parsing helpers verbatim. The chapter introduces no new RTL
and reuses the spi_1lane.bin bitstream directly. Block 5 (`presc=5`
